{"tid":413784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[窮人恩物]大學生首置上車盤售價最低約588萬元","createTime":"2017-09-25T16:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T04:05:18.000Z","uid":50386,"like":4,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc08b8ea304b5dfddb37b76827dd942a7d3982f0","tid":413784,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】新世界宣布撥出屯門新盤「天生樓」一成半單位，作大學生首置上車盤，首期最多為樓價兩成。<br />\n<br />\n位於屯門鄉事會路的天生樓是單幢式項目，合共100個單位，新世界會把其中15個作為大學生首置上車盤。單位面積422呎至575呎，兩房及三房單位，售價最低約588萬元 。<br />\n<br />\n新世界表示，這批單位首期為樓價約一至兩成，發展商會代繳從價印花稅，預留售予畢業最少兩至三年的大學生，兩個月後公布銷售細則，最快12月推售。"},{"pid":"3b67d789a6e301b11d2c9dcf51e4beec3fab4fc9","tid":413784,"uid":119979,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:20:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">最低<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">約</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最低不特止, 仲要約 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4dd567ddffdc86af58cc15a19dde435e57969c","tid":413784,"uid":54264,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"差唔多成600萬既上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd193289de2b354b6656cb4d649fac849c2f0c0","tid":413784,"uid":20241,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"10000蚊6折市價月租貨櫃屋<br />\n600萬後生仔上車盤<br />\n根本香港班上層已離撚曬地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88851f5d5a05b5eaeaf8e720078ef1ad242ac9e7","tid":413784,"uid":149361,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:24:38.000Z","msg":"劫金鋪都未必籌到筆錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89108c60ee3d172647ceb79692f1003036592ad","tid":413784,"uid":42921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"謝主隆恩丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"